snippet: As three-time defending champion Novak Djokovic held the Australian Open trophy in a photo shoot before Friday's draw, he joked that having his fingerprints on it may in some way help him win the title for a fourth consecutive year....

headline.print_headline: AO: Nadal, Murray, Federer All in the Same Half
headline.main: AO: Nadal, Murray, Federer All in the Same Half

lead_paragraph: As three-time defending champion Novak Djokovic held the Australian Open trophy in a photo shoot before Friday's draw, he joked that having his fingerprints on it may in some way help him win the title for a fourth consecutive year.
